sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant API as ModelMeshApi<br/>8033/TCP gRPC<br/>TLS + mTLS (opt)
    participant MM as SidecarModelMesh<br/>LRU Cache
    participant Runtime as Model Runtime<br/>8085/TCP or UDS<br/>plaintext gRPC
    participant LL as Litelinks<br/>8080/TCP Thrift<br/>TLS + mTLS (opt)
    participant RemoteMM as Remote ModelMesh<br/>Instance
    participant RemoteRT as Remote Model<br/>Runtime
    participant etcd as etcd<br/>2379/TCP gRPC<br/>TLS (opt)
    participant VMgr as VModelManager

    Note over Client,etcd: Flow 1: Model Inference Request (Cache Hit)
    Client->>API: gRPC Inference Request<br/>TLS + mTLS (optional)
    API->>MM: Route request (in-process)
    MM->>MM: LRU Cache Lookup (hit)
    MM->>Runtime: Forward to runtime<br/>gRPC :8085 or UDS
    Runtime-->>MM: Prediction Result
    MM-->>API: Response
    API-->>Client: gRPC Response

    Note over Client,etcd: Flow 1b: Model Inference Request (Cache Miss - Forward)
    Client->>API: gRPC Inference Request
    API->>MM: Route request (in-process)
    MM->>MM: LRU Cache Lookup (miss)
    MM->>LL: Forward to remote instance<br/>Thrift/TCP :8080
    LL->>RemoteMM: applyModelMulti RPC<br/>TLS + mTLS (optional)
    RemoteMM->>RemoteRT: Forward to runtime<br/>gRPC :8085 or UDS
    RemoteRT-->>RemoteMM: Prediction Result
    RemoteMM-->>LL: Response
    LL-->>MM: Response
    MM-->>API: Response
    API-->>Client: gRPC Response

    Note over Client,etcd: Flow 2: Model Registration and Loading
    Client->>API: registerModel RPC<br/>gRPC :8033
    API->>MM: Register (in-process)
    MM->>etcd: Write ModelRecord<br/>gRPC :2379
    etcd-->>MM: Watch notification<br/>(placed instance)
    MM->>Runtime: loadModel RPC<br/>gRPC :8085 or UDS
    Runtime-->>MM: Load complete
    MM->>etcd: Update ModelRecord<br/>(add instance ID)
    MM-->>API: Registration confirmed
    API-->>Client: Success response

    Note over Client,etcd: Flow 3: Virtual Model Transition (Zero-Downtime)
    Client->>API: setVModel RPC<br/>gRPC :8033
    API->>VMgr: Set vmodel (in-process)
    VMgr->>etcd: Write VModelRecord<br/>gRPC :2379
    VMgr->>MM: registerModel (target)
    MM->>Runtime: loadModel (target)<br/>gRPC :8085 or UDS
    Runtime-->>MM: Target loaded
    VMgr->>etcd: Atomic swap<br/>active ↔ target
    VMgr->>MM: unregisterModel (old active)
    VMgr-->>API: Transition complete
    API-->>Client: Success response
